StatusTabDescription: Here are the statuses for the document:
ShareDocumentDescription: Share document with the client, send an OTP via email: {{otp}}
SaveChangesDesc: Save the current changes and create a new revision.
DiscardChangesDesc: Drop the current changes and start from the original.
NoRevisionsFound: There are no revisions so far, to create a revision you need to save a version of the preventive.
ChangeToSignup: Don't have an account? Sign Up
UnlockDocumentDescription: This is a private document, we sent an email with an OTP (one time password), please use that to unlock the view.
ErrorSavingDocument: There was an error saving your document.
UploadFilesSectionDescription: To delete a file click the bin icon and save the document.
HandleDiscardDescription: Discard the changes you have made to the document.
HandleSaveDescription: Save the current changes to the document.
HandleSubmitDescription: Submit the document for review or processing.
HandleGeneratePDFDescription: Generate a PDF version of the document.
HandleRejectDescription: Reject the current document and notify the relevant parties.
InternalNotesDescription: Internal notes are for admin and users only, will not be seen by clients at any time. Will be later on further editable to keep track of progress.
PreviewQuoteTemplateDescription: The submission will generate a webpage form, further editable as shared document with client. Once created an OTP (one time password) will be sent to the client's email.
RejectDocumentDescription: Make the document invalid, turn into read only.
YouNeedToBeAdmin: You need to be admin to execute this action
DocumentCreatedMessage: Document created, you can now view your document in the documents list. ID (hash): {{hash}}
QuoteListPageHeadDesc: In here you find the PDFs documents to download
SignatureSectionDescription: Date and signature, you can keep it or upload a new one

CreateQuotePageDescription: With this form you can create a template that can be later edited by you and the client.
OpenDocumentQuoteDesc: This is a form that will allow you to create a preventive object referred to as a document. This form will enable you to choose a client, select products, and add notes for internal use by users and admins.
HomepageDocumentsCardDesc: These are documents, which are like editable webpages shared with the client and other users. They can be used to refine the quote, containing detailed information such as history logs, markdown for product descriptions, and more features.
HomepageQuotesCardDesc: The quote list contains the final PDFs generated by a document. The document shapes a quote, which is the static, definitive preventive quote.
HomepageUsersCardDesc: This section provides typical CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) functionalities for managing users.
HomepageProductCardDesc: This section provides typical CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) functionalities for managing products.
HomepageClientsCardDesc: This section provides typical CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) functionalities for managing clients.

HowToOpenAQuoteProcess: How to create a quote, here 's the process:
Step1: 1. Generate an editable document that will be shared with the client.
Step2: 2. Once you open a document, you can find it in the document list.
Step3: 3. Once the document is signed, it can be created as a PDF quote.
Step4: 4. Once the document is a PDF quote, you can find it in the quote list.
